# Normalize line endings. Text files are stored as LF in the repo AND checked
# out as LF in the working tree (eol=lf overrides core.autocrlf on Windows),
# so tools that write LF (Prettier, ESLint --fix) no longer create CRLF churn.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never apply EOL conversion or text diffing.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary
*.ico binary
*.svg text eol=lf
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.pdf binary
